      "id": "PopularPost186755",
      "post_content": "[Obelisk of Grixis](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Obelisk of Grixis) can be played on the same turn as a land, and it's an artifact, which is a boon all to itself.  \nBut yeah, if you're playing grixis, use this card instead of the Obelisk. It doesn't screw you over if you get it instead of basic lands.",
